{"type": "article", "id": 15220, "title": "关于智能家居和智能硬件，有这 30 个愚蠢想象被人实现了 | 每天还有一个 List", "description": "愚蠢的设计有着各种不同的愚蠢……", "date": "2015-09-27T08:00:00Z", "super_tag": "", "tags": [{"id": 821, "name": "智能家居"}, {"id": 2538, "name": "智能硬件"}, {"id": 536, "name": "三星"}, {"id": 683, "name": "LG"}], "category": 4, "author": 73517, "comment_count": 69, "praise_count": 466, "image": "img/article/long_show/20160606153317y3cSsZuOEQeC1l6T.jpg", "contents": "\n\n<div>\r\n</div>\r\n<h2>\r\n\t<span style=\"text-align:start;\">记录你运动量的椅子</span> \r\n</h2>\r\n<p>\r\n\t<span style=\"text-align:start;\"></span> \r\n</p>\r\n<p style=\"text-align:center;\">\r\n\t<img src=\"img/uploads/20160606153303BEPsY5Q72pAWL9lx.jpg\" title=\"Tao Chair 椅子\" alt=\"Tao Chair 椅子\" data-ratio=\"0.73310424\" data-format=\"jpeg\"><span><em>Tao Chair 椅子</em></span> \r\n</p>\r\n<p>\r\n</p>\r\n<div>\r\n</div>\r\n<div>\r\n\t<span style=\"text-align:start;\"><a href=\"http://www.gizmag.com/taochair-living-room-workout/35542/\">TAO-Wellness 的这把椅子</a>，能记录你旋转、按压、抬腿时消耗的卡路里。不过你在椅子上最耗体能的运动大概就是抖腿了吧。</span> \r\n</div>\r\n<div>\r\n</div>\r\n<h2>\r\n\t<span style=\"text-align:start;\">把平板挂头上自拍的帽子</span> \r\n</h2>\r\n<p>\r\n\t<span style=\"text-align:start;\"></span> \r\n</p>\r\n<p style=\"text-align:center;\">\r\n\t<img src=\"img/uploads/201606061533034pAPqIcuHF8kMGvC.jpg\" title=\"Acer 自拍帽\" alt=\"Acer 自拍帽\" data-ratio=\"0.66666667\" data-format=\"jpeg\"><span><em>Acer 自拍帽</em></span> \r\n</p>\r\n<p style=\"text-align:left;\">\r\n\t<span><span style=\"text-align:start;\">大家好，这是宏碁想到的好点子——</span><a href=\"http://wtvox.com/iot-startups/top-10-worst-wearable-tech-devices-so-far/\">在你面前吊一块平板电脑自拍</a><span style=\"text-align:start;\">。想象一下带着宽沿帽，一边走路平板一边前后甩的样子，什么优雅自拍的心情都没有了不是吗？</span></span> \r\n</p>\r\n<p>\r\n</p>\r\n<div>\r\n</div>\r\n<p>\r\n</p>\r\n<h2>\r\n\t<span style=\"text-align:start;\">看一眼就能解锁的眼球扫描仪</span> \r\n</h2>\r\n<p>\r\n\t<span style=\"text-align:start;\"></span> \r\n</p>\r\n<p style=\"text-align:center;\">\r\n\t<img src=\"img/uploads/20160606153304cQNOw3vfbxdWFGyg.jpg\" title=\"EyeLock 摄像头\" alt=\"EyeLock 摄像头\" data-ratio=\"0.74853801\" data-format=\"jpeg\"><span><em>E</em><em>yeLock 眼球摄像头</em></span> \r\n</p>\r\n<p>\r\n</p>\r\n<div>\r\n</div>\r\n<div>\r\n\t<span style=\"text-align:start;\"><a href=\"http://www.zdnet.com/pictures/11-born-to-fail-worst-gadgets-at-ces-2014/\">EyeLock 公司出了一个摄像头</a>，唯一的功能是拍你的眼球然后自动输入电脑登录密码。问题是，万一你不小心瞄了它一眼呢？</span> \r\n</div>\r\n<div>\r\n</div>\r\n<h2>\r\n\t<span style=\"text-align:start;\">要你电击自己的手环</span> \r\n</h2>\r\n<p>\r\n\t<span style=\"text-align:start;\"></span> \r\n</p>\r\n<p style=\"text-align:center;\">\r\n\t<img src=\"img/uploads/20160606153304QRkMVF8JAOBvt7SU.jpg\" title=\"Pavlok 手环\" alt=\"Pavlok 手环\" data-ratio=\"0.61302682\" data-format=\"jpeg\"><span><em>Pavlok 手环</em></span> \r\n</p>\r\n<p>\r\n</p>\r\n<div>\r\n</div>\r\n<div>\r\n\t<span style=\"text-align:start;\"><a href=\"http://www.businessinsider.com/pavlok-bracelet-shocks-you-2014-11\">Pavlok 手环</a>的作用和马戏团的鞭子差不多，想通过电击帮你戒掉暴饮暴食、吸烟之类的习惯。先不说电击虐待人类这功能是不是有争议，重点是这手环根本不知道你有没有违戒，你得“自觉”电击自己，天呐！</span> \r\n</div>\r\n<div>\r\n</div>\r\n<h2>\r\n\t<span style=\"text-align:start;\">不能下水的智能戒指</span> \r\n</h2>\r\n<p>\r\n\t<span style=\"text-align:start;\"></span> \r\n</p>\r\n<p style=\"text-align:center;\">\r\n\t<img src=\"img/uploads/2016060615330546rLOo2c83deDjN0.jpg\" title=\"Ring 智能戒指\" alt=\"Ring 智能戒指\" data-ratio=\"0.66666667\" data-format=\"jpeg\"><span><em>Ring 智能戒指</em></span> \r\n</p>\r\n<p>\r\n</p>\r\n<div>\r\n</div>\r\n<div>\r\n\t<span style=\"text-align:start;\">智能戒指这种产品本来能做的就不多了，<a href=\"http://www.kickstarter.com/projects/1761670738/ring-shortcut-everything/description\">Logbar 公司的这款戒指</a>竟然不防水，洗手都要摘下，用它可能比用手环还麻烦。</span> \r\n</div>\r\n<div>\r\n</div>\r\n<h2>\r\n\t<span style=\"text-align:start;\">配备触摸屏的耳机</span> \r\n</h2>\r\n<p>\r\n\t<span style=\"text-align:start;\"></span> \r\n</p>\r\n<p style=\"text-align:center;\">\r\n\t<img src=\"img/uploads/20160606153305U93nrFNKlqiPax7Z.jpg\" title=\"Vinci 耳机\" alt=\"Vinci 耳机\" data-ratio=\"0.7\" data-format=\"jpeg\"><span><em>Vinci 耳机</em></span> \r\n</p>\r\n<p>\r\n</p>\r\n<div>\r\n</div>\r\n<div>\r\n\t<span style=\"text-align:start;\"><a href=\"http://headphone.zol.com.cn/522/5228832.html\">Vinci 公司在耳机上加了块触摸屏</a>，左右滑动可以切换曲目，但如果你想听特定的一首歌？那么得把耳机摘下来。</span> \r\n</div>\r\n<div>\r\n</div>\r\n<h2>\r\n\t<span style=\"text-align:start;\">能测空气质量的自行车</span> \r\n</h2>\r\n<p>\r\n\t<span style=\"text-align:start;\"></span> \r\n</p>\r\n<p style=\"text-align:center;\">\r\n\t<img src=\"img/uploads/20160606153306Xz4ewyqvjpFsAJGT.jpg\" title=\"乐视超级自行车\" alt=\"乐视超级自行车\" data-ratio=\"0.66252588\" data-format=\"jpeg\"><span><em>乐视超级自行车</em></span> \r\n</p>\r\n<p>\r\n</p>\r\n<div>\r\n</div>\r\n<p>\r\n\t<span style=\"text-align:start;\">查空气质量的工作，本来是在推车出门前就要做好的。但这辆<a href=\"http://www.qdaily.com/articles/13379.html\">乐视自行车</a>，要你在骑行中实时看空气质量，怎么有种让你成为人肉空气检测站的即视感。与其生产出来，不如放在 PPT 里帮乐视提升股价吧。</span> \r\n</p>\r\n<div>\r\n</div>\r\n<h2>\r\n\t<span style=\"text-align:start;\">可以做充电坞的花盆</span> \r\n</h2>\r\n<p>\r\n\t<span style=\"text-align:start;\"></span> \r\n</p>\r\n<p style=\"text-align:center;\">\r\n\t<img src=\"img/uploads/20160606153306IcH3q4xQlVZNgiv5.jpg\" title=\"微花园的花盆\" alt=\"微花园的花盆\" data-ratio=\"0.58055556\" data-format=\"jpeg\"><span><em>微花园的花盆</em></span> \r\n</p>\r\n<p>\r\n</p>\r\n<div>\r\n</div>\r\n<div>\r\n\t<span style=\"text-align:start;\">这个产品叫<a href=\"http://www.leiphone.com/news/201406/d-winmartdesign-smart-garden.html\">微花园</a>。如果要给手机充电，你得先把花盆接上电源，然后将手机充电线接上花盆背面的 USB 口......</span> \r\n</div>\r\n<div>\r\n</div>\r\n<h2>\r\n\t<span style=\"text-align:start;\">和你走路一个速度的交通工具</span> \r\n</h2>\r\n<p>\r\n\t<span style=\"text-align:start;\"></span> \r\n</p>\r\n<p style=\"text-align:center;\">\r\n\t<img src=\"img/uploads/20160606153307tbqPZlCvHUQWE935.jpg\" title=\"本田 Uni-Cub 电动椅\" alt=\"本田 Uni-Cub 电动椅\" data-ratio=\"0.71829405\" data-format=\"jpeg\"><span><em>本田 Uni-Cub 电动椅</em></span> \r\n</p>\r\n<p>\r\n</p>\r\n<div>\r\n</div>\r\n<div>\r\n\t<span style=\"text-align:start;\"><a href=\"http://www.qdaily.com/articles/12963.html\">本田这电动座椅</a>，想让你坐在凳子上，动动屁股就能走，不过它的速度跟你走路差不多。</span> \r\n</div>\r\n<div>\r\n</div>\r\n<h2>\r\n\t<span style=\"text-align:start;\">问你要邮箱密码并泄露出去的智能冰箱</span> \r\n</h2>\r\n<p>\r\n\t<span style=\"text-align:start;\"></span> \r\n</p>\r\n<p style=\"text-align:center;\">\r\n\t<img src=\"img/uploads/201606061533078UstquWHmKb41pNI.jpg\" title=\"三星智能冰箱\" alt=\"三星智能冰箱\" data-ratio=\"0.75029308\" data-format=\"jpeg\"><span><em>三星智能冰箱</em></span> \r\n</p>\r\n<p>\r\n</p>\r\n<div>\r\n</div>\r\n<div>\r\n\t<span style=\"text-align:start;\"><a href=\"http://www.theregister.co.uk/2015/08/24/smart_fridge_security_fubar/\">三星推出了一款智能冰箱</a>，能联网、能发邮件、还会泄露你的邮箱密码......</span> \r\n</div>\r\n<div>\r\n</div>\r\n<h2>\r\n\t<span style=\"text-align:start;\">盖在智能手机屏幕上的物理键盘</span> \r\n</h2>\r\n<p>\r\n\t<span style=\"text-align:start;\"></span> \r\n</p>\r\n<p style=\"text-align:center;\">\r\n\t<img src=\"img/uploads/20160606153308HNQXOfAUPaqED68j.jpg\" title=\"三星 Galaxy S6 Edge+ 键盘\" alt=\"三星 Galaxy S6 Edge+ 键盘\" data-ratio=\"0.56203704\" data-format=\"jpeg\"><span><em>三星 Galaxy S6 Edge+ 键盘</em></span> \r\n</p>\r\n<p>\r\n</p>\r\n<div>\r\n</div>\r\n<div>\r\n\t<span style=\"text-align:start;\">买<a href=\"http://www.independent.co.uk/life-style/gadgets-and-tech/news/samsung-galaxy-s6-edge-keyboard-accessory-draws-nostalgia-mockery-10455689.html\">三星一个超大的屏幕</a>，就为了给键盘盖住。</span> \r\n</div>\r\n<div>\r\n</div>\r\n<h2>\r\n\t<span style=\"text-align:start;\">内置手电筒的移动电源</span> \r\n</h2>\r\n<p>\r\n\t<span style=\"text-align:start;\"></span> \r\n</p>\r\n<p style=\"text-align:center;\">\r\n\t<img src=\"img/uploads/20160606153308qgnHaLzbphUu7xei.jpg\" title=\"JNT 移动电源\" alt=\"JNT 移动电源\" data-ratio=\"0.71428571\" data-format=\"jpeg\"><span><em>JNT 移动电源</em></span> \r\n</p>\r\n<p>\r\n</p>\r\n<div>\r\n</div>\r\n<div>\r\n\t<span style=\"text-align:start;\"><a href=\"http://www.mobilespowerbank.com/sale-4382921-18650-li-ion-lithium-ion-portable-power-bank-4000mah-mobile-charger-with-led-light.html\">JNT 公司的移动电源</a>内置手电筒，问题是你并不常用。如果经常用到，你机不离身的手机就有此功能了。</span> \r\n</div>\r\n<div>\r\n</div>\r\n<h2>\r\n\t<span style=\"text-align:start;\">收到短信就点火的灶台</span> \r\n</h2>\r\n<p>\r\n\t<span style=\"text-align:start;\"></span> \r\n</p>\r\n<p style=\"text-align:center;\">\r\n\t<img src=\"img/uploads/20160606153308va9SCscMmJfXTyNl.jpg\" title=\"AGA 智能灶台\" alt=\"AGA 智能灶台\" data-ratio=\"0.66666667\" data-format=\"jpeg\"><span><em>AGA 智能灶台</em></span> \r\n</p>\r\n<p>\r\n</p>\r\n<div>\r\n</div>\r\n<div>\r\n\t<span style=\"text-align:start;\">你在外面把家里 <a href=\"http://www.jetsocial.co.uk/the-aga-cooker-that-can-be-controlled-with-your-phone/\">AGA 牌的灶台</a>的火打开了，但除了想要纵火之外实在想不到什么使用场景，难道是谁要帮你炒菜然后不懂开炉子吗？</span> \r\n</div>\r\n<div>\r\n</div>\r\n<h2>\r\n\t<span style=\"text-align:start;\">用手机应用远程操作的智能烤箱</span> \r\n</h2>\r\n<p>\r\n\t<span style=\"text-align:start;\"></span> \r\n</p>\r\n<p style=\"text-align:center;\">\r\n\t<img src=\"img/uploads/20160606153309iCQ6GLFf8J91ZhRq.jpg\" title=\"LG 智能烤箱\" alt=\"LG 智能烤箱\" data-ratio=\"0.66184074\" data-format=\"jpeg\"><span><em>LG 智能烤箱</em></span> \r\n</p>\r\n<p>\r\n</p>\r\n<div>\r\n</div>\r\n<div>\r\n\t<span style=\"text-align:start;\">要用 <a href=\"http://metroplexbbq.blogspot.com/2012/07/lg-lightwave-oven-with-remote.html\">LG 的这个智能烤箱</a>，你还得买一个异常先进的机器人帮你把菜放进烤箱。</span> \r\n</div>\r\n<div>\r\n</div>\r\n<h2>\r\n\t<span style=\"text-align:start;\">套在喉咙上测你吃了多少的智能颈环</span> \r\n</h2>\r\n<p>\r\n\t<span style=\"text-align:start;\"></span> \r\n</p>\r\n<p style=\"text-align:center;\">\r\n\t<img src=\"img/uploads/20160606153309L7uETGIbgr0h1mKQ.jpg\" title=\"WearSens 智能颈环\" alt=\"WearSens 智能颈环\" data-ratio=\"0.56203704\" data-format=\"jpeg\"><span><em>WearSens 智能颈环</em></span> \r\n</p>\r\n<p>\r\n</p>\r\n<div>\r\n</div>\r\n<div>\r\n\t<span style=\"text-align:start;\">这<a href=\"http://www.cbsnews.com/news/could-this-necklace-help-you-lose-weight/\">颈环是加州大学洛杉矶分校研发</a>的，检测你的吞咽，但它根本弄不清楚你在吃什么。</span> \r\n</div>\r\n<div>\r\n</div>\r\n<h2>\r\n\t<span style=\"text-align:start;\">用手机调节镜片颜色的墨镜</span> \r\n</h2>\r\n<p>\r\n\t<span style=\"text-align:start;\"></span> \r\n</p>\r\n<p style=\"text-align:center;\">\r\n\t<img src=\"img/uploads/20160606153310bIRSVZdmWuJE6LBA.jpg\" title=\"Skugga 智能太阳镜\" alt=\"Skugga 智能太阳镜\" data-ratio=\"0.48888889\" data-format=\"jpeg\"><span><em>Skugga 智能太阳镜</em></span> \r\n</p>\r\n<p>\r\n</p>\r\n<div>\r\n</div>\r\n<div>\r\n\t<span style=\"text-align:start;\">戴上 <a href=\"http://www.qdaily.com/articles/11828.html\">Skugga Eyewear 的太阳镜</a>，调一次镜片颜色，就得掏一次手机。对了，其实自动变色的眼镜已经卖了好多年了......</span> \r\n</div>\r\n<div>\r\n</div>\r\n<h2>\r\n\t<span style=\"text-align:start;\">植入完整键盘的电视遥控器</span> \r\n</h2>\r\n<p>\r\n\t<span style=\"text-align:start;\"></span> \r\n</p>\r\n<p style=\"text-align:center;\">\r\n\t<img src=\"img/uploads/20160606153310Xa6bSu1vngAzdHqN.jpg\" title=\"索尼的电视遥控器\" alt=\"索尼的电视遥控器\" data-ratio=\"0.67222222\" data-format=\"jpeg\"><span><em>索尼的电视遥控器</em></span> \r\n</p>\r\n<p>\r\n</p>\r\n<div>\r\n</div>\r\n<div>\r\n\t<span style=\"text-align:start;\">索尼为第一代 <a href=\"http://buchnotes.com/2010/11/05/sonys-google-tv-remote-leaves-a-lot-to-be-desired/\">Google TV 机顶盒准备的全键盘遥控器</a>，超过 70 个按键。问题是你要对着电视打多少字？</span> \r\n</div>\r\n<div>\r\n</div>\r\n<h2>\r\n\t<span style=\"text-align:start;\">用 LED 灯模拟火苗的电磁炉锅</span> \r\n</h2>\r\n<p>\r\n\t<span style=\"text-align:start;\"></span> \r\n</p>\r\n<p style=\"text-align:center;\">\r\n\t<img src=\"img/uploads/20160606153311Q4dxPg57rsoEUDzF.jpg\" title=\"三星的含 LED 灯的电磁炉锅\" alt=\"三星的含 LED 灯的电磁炉锅\" data-ratio=\"0.53611111\" data-format=\"jpeg\"><span><em>三星的含 LED 灯的电磁炉锅</em></span> \r\n</p>\r\n<p>\r\n</p>\r\n<div>\r\n</div>\r\n<div>\r\n\t<span style=\"text-align:start;\">这真的是电磁炉，<a href=\"http://www.gizmodo.com.au/2014/10/fake-led-flames-indicate-how-hot-samsungs-new-induction-stove-gets/\">三星花了很大的力气</a>，就是为了给你模拟明火烹饪的快乐。但这是个悖论，但如果你要模拟明火还为什么要用电磁炉？用</span><span style=\"text-align:start;\">了电磁炉看明火，好看吗？并不。有用吗？也并不。</span> \r\n</div>\r\n<div>\r\n</div>\r\n<h2>\r\n\t<span style=\"text-align:start;\">能且只能被手机控制的智能灯泡</span> \r\n</h2>\r\n<p>\r\n\t<span style=\"text-align:start;\"></span> \r\n</p>\r\n<p style=\"text-align:center;\">\r\n\t<img src=\"img/uploads/201606061533112Gm1AScfaBVryeo9.jpg\" title=\"iMagic 智能灯\" alt=\"iMagic 智能灯\" data-ratio=\"0.66296296\" data-format=\"jpeg\"><span><em>iMagic 智能灯</em></span> \r\n</p>\r\n<p>\r\n</p>\r\n<div>\r\n</div>\r\n<div>\r\n\t<span style=\"text-align:start;\">使用 <a href=\"http://www.qdaily.com/articles/11828.html\">iMagic 智能灯泡</a>可能是这样的场景：半夜，灯没开，找不到手机；没找到手机，不能开灯……</span> \r\n</div>\r\n<div>\r\n</div>\r\n<h2>\r\n\t<span style=\"text-align:start;\">用扫码器记录你用过什么商品的垃圾桶</span> \r\n</h2>\r\n<p>\r\n\t<span style=\"text-align:start;\"></span> \r\n</p>\r\n<p style=\"text-align:center;\">\r\n\t<img src=\"img/uploads/201606061533118KNZ9M5kPqwfCGHx.jpg\" title=\"GeniCan 垃圾桶\" alt=\"GeniCan 垃圾桶\" data-ratio=\"1.25\" data-format=\"jpeg\"><span><em>GeniCan 垃圾桶</em></span> \r\n</p>\r\n<p>\r\n</p>\r\n<div>\r\n</div>\r\n<div>\r\n\t<span style=\"text-align:start;\">往 <a href=\"http://www.indiegogo.com/projects/genican-your-garbage-can-just-got-smart#/story\">GeniCan 垃圾桶</a>丢垃圾？你得先把包装盒找到，然后扫码，再放进桶里。</span> \r\n</div>\r\n<div>\r\n</div>\r\n<h2>\r\n\t<span style=\"text-align:start;\">没有智能家居的智能家居控制器</span> \r\n</h2>\r\n<p>\r\n\t<span style=\"text-align:start;\"></span> \r\n</p>\r\n<p style=\"text-align:center;\">\r\n\t<img src=\"img/uploads/20160606153312Xv0tkfBgQEmihuMj.jpg\" title=\"Google OnHub 路由器\" alt=\"Google OnHub 路由器\" data-ratio=\"0.59981256\" data-format=\"jpeg\"><span><em>Google OnHub 路由器</em></span> \r\n</p>\r\n<p>\r\n</p>\r\n<div>\r\n</div>\r\n<div>\r\n\t<span style=\"text-align:start;\">装载 Google 最新物联网系统的 <a href=\"http://www.qdaily.com/articles/13729.html\">OnHub 智能路由器</a>来了，但被它控制的智能家居还一件都没有。</span> \r\n</div>\r\n<div>\r\n</div>\r\n<h2>\r\n\t<span style=\"text-align:start;\">让你对着它看电视的智能冰箱</span> \r\n</h2>\r\n<p>\r\n\t<span style=\"text-align:start;\"></span> \r\n</p>\r\n<p style=\"text-align:center;\">\r\n\t<img src=\"img/uploads/20160606153312hDTr05maPJxd2Evy.jpg\" title=\"配备电视机的 LG 冰箱\" alt=\"配备电视机的 LG 冰箱\" data-ratio=\"0.99224806\" data-format=\"jpeg\"><span><em>配备电视机的 LG 冰箱</em></span> \r\n</p>\r\n<p>\r\n</p>\r\n<div>\r\n</div>\r\n<div>\r\n\t<span style=\"text-align:start;\">委屈你了，本来想从冰箱拿一瓶牛奶喝，结果对着 <a href=\"http://www.engadget.com/2006/11/03/lgs-dual-screen-hdtv-equipped-refrigerator/\">LG 冰箱内嵌的小电视</a>看了一集美剧。</span> \r\n</div>\r\n<div>\r\n</div>\r\n<h2>\r\n\t<span style=\"text-align:start;\">将鸡蛋数量显示在手机上的智能鸡蛋架</span> \r\n</h2>\r\n<p>\r\n\t<span style=\"text-align:start;\"></span> \r\n</p>\r\n<p style=\"text-align:center;\">\r\n\t<img src=\"img/uploads/20160606153313gfS8KxYNeFDl14iv.jpg\" title=\"Egg Minder 智能鸡蛋架\" alt=\"Egg Minder 智能鸡蛋架\" data-ratio=\"0.56203704\" data-format=\"jpeg\"><span><em>Egg Minder 智能鸡蛋架</em></span> \r\n</p>\r\n<p>\r\n</p>\r\n<div>\r\n</div>\r\n<div>\r\n\t<span style=\"text-align:start;\">除非你要在冰箱里放上数不清的鸡蛋，或者这些鸡蛋自己变成小鸡走了，否则<a href=\"http://www.standard.co.uk/lifestyle/london-life/london-s-best-fridge-tech-9810436.html\">这个能让你知道自己有多少鸡蛋的智能硬件</a>还有什么用？有个更加快捷的办法，叫打开冰箱门。</span> \r\n</div>\r\n<div>\r\n</div>\r\n<h2>\r\n\t<span style=\"text-align:start;\">不防水的智能水杯</span> \r\n</h2>\r\n<p>\r\n\t<span style=\"text-align:start;\"></span> \r\n</p>\r\n<p style=\"text-align:center;\">\r\n\t<img src=\"img/uploads/201606061533135xaqMpRemFwKBJyE.jpg\" title=\"麦开智能水杯\" alt=\"麦开智能水杯\" data-ratio=\"0.75029308\" data-format=\"jpeg\"><span><em>麦开智能水杯</em></span> \r\n</p>\r\n<p>\r\n</p>\r\n<div>\r\n</div>\r\n<div>\r\n\t<span style=\"text-align:start;\"><a href=\"http://www.leiphone.com/news/201509/7eiS1aRvo9bWODmm.html\">麦开的这个智能水杯</a>竟然不能直接冲洗，这真的是水杯？</span> \r\n</div>\r\n<div>\r\n</div>\r\n<h2>\r\n\t<span style=\"text-align:start;\">自带打火机的充电宝</span> \r\n</h2>\r\n<p>\r\n\t<span style=\"text-align:start;\"></span> \r\n</p>\r\n<p style=\"text-align:center;\">\r\n\t<img src=\"img/uploads/20160606153314DHZ1e04uhzRWIbOS.jpg\" title=\"内置打火机的 Zvedeng 充电宝\" alt=\"内置打火机的 Zvedeng 充电宝\" data-ratio=\"1.0\" data-format=\"jpeg\"><span><em>内置打火机的 Zvedeng 充电宝</em></span> \r\n</p>\r\n<p>\r\n</p>\r\n<div>\r\n</div>\r\n<div>\r\n\t<span style=\"text-align:start;\">这个名为 <a href=\"http://www.amazon.co.uk/Zvedeng-Waterproof-Shockproof-Cigarette-Emergency-black/dp/B0107TX2UI\">Zvedeng 的充电宝</a>估计能引发新时尚——手指夹着一根香烟，举起充电宝，深吸一口，吐出烟圈。想想也是挺特（yu）别（chun）的，哦，禁止使用充电宝的理由又多了一项。</span> \r\n</div>\r\n<div>\r\n</div>\r\n<h2>\r\n\t<span style=\"text-align:start;\">所有只能检测运动状态的手环</span> \r\n</h2>\r\n<p>\r\n\t<span style=\"text-align:start;\"></span> \r\n</p>\r\n<p style=\"text-align:center;\">\r\n\t<img src=\"img/uploads/20160606153314wIflokPW2F53tbMO.jpg\" title=\"运动手环\" alt=\"运动手环\" data-ratio=\"0.66296296\" data-format=\"jpeg\"><span><em>运动手环</em></span> \r\n</p>\r\n<p>\r\n</p>\r\n<p>\r\n\t<span style=\"text-align:start;\"></span> \r\n</p>\r\n<div>\r\n</div>\r\n<div>\r\n\t<span style=\"text-align:start;\"><a href=\"http://www.fitbit.com/au\">这些手环</a>可以测你的运动距离、心率、步数。但今天的智能手机同样能实现所有这些功能，我为什么还要买手环？</span> \r\n</div>\r\n<div>\r\n</div>\r\n<h2>\r\n\t<span style=\"text-align:start;\">能上网的冰箱</span> \r\n</h2>\r\n<p>\r\n\t<span style=\"text-align:start;\"></span> \r\n</p>\r\n<p style=\"text-align:center;\">\r\n\t<img src=\"img/uploads/20160606153314wCpxh0R4YMelfTnu.jpg\" title=\"内置浏览器的三星智能冰箱\" alt=\"内置浏览器的三星智能冰箱\" data-ratio=\"0.74941452\" data-format=\"jpeg\"><span><em>内置浏览器的三星智能冰箱</em></span> \r\n</p>\r\n<p>\r\n</p>\r\n<div>\r\n</div>\r\n<div>\r\n\t<span style=\"text-align:start;\">有谁打算拿牛奶出来喝的同时，顺便用<a href=\"http://www.samsung.com/us/appliances/refrigerators/RF28HMELBSR/AA\">三星智能冰箱</a>内置的浏览器开个网页冲浪？</span> \r\n</div>\r\n<div>\r\n</div>\r\n<h2>\r\n\t<span style=\"text-align:start;\">记录你蹲马桶时长的智能马桶</span> \r\n</h2>\r\n<p>\r\n\t<span style=\"text-align:start;\"></span> \r\n</p>\r\n<p style=\"text-align:center;\">\r\n\t<img src=\"img/uploads/20160606153315d0FH4qrSbVn5plLy.jpg\" title=\"智能马桶\" alt=\"智能马桶\" data-ratio=\"1.024\" data-format=\"jpeg\"><span><em>智能马桶</em></span> \r\n</p>\r\n<p>\r\n</p>\r\n<p>\r\n\t<span style=\"text-align:start;\"></span> \r\n</p>\r\n<div>\r\n</div>\r\n<div>\r\n\t<span style=\"text-align:start;\">这个 <a href=\"http://www.internetofuselessthings.io/\">Throne Master 马桶</a>要记下你的使用马桶时长，还要和家人比赛，决出“蹲马桶大王”，这难道不是斗谁在便秘吗？</span> \r\n</div>\r\n<div>\r\n</div>\r\n<h2>\r\n\t<span style=\"text-align:start;\">记下你阅读页码的智能书签</span> \r\n</h2>\r\n<p>\r\n\t<span style=\"text-align:start;\"></span> \r\n</p>\r\n<p style=\"text-align:center;\">\r\n\t<img src=\"img/uploads/20160606153315iE8hHQozdBTVSwt6.jpg\" title=\"BookMk 智能书签\" alt=\"BookMk 智能书签\" data-ratio=\"0.71991001\" data-format=\"jpeg\"><span><em>BookMk 智能书签</em></span> \r\n</p>\r\n<p>\r\n</p>\r\n<div>\r\n</div>\r\n<div>\r\n\t<span style=\"text-align:start;\">“我上次看到哪了？”掏出手机，打开应用，请求查看阅读进度，收到提示短信，然后翻书......感谢有你，<a href=\"http://www.internetofuselessthings.io/\">BookMk 智能书签</a>。</span> \r\n</div>\r\n<div>\r\n</div>\r\n<h2>\r\n\t<span style=\"text-align:start;\">可以看电子书的智能冰箱</span> \r\n</h2>\r\n<p>\r\n\t<span style=\"text-align:start;\"></span> \r\n</p>\r\n<p style=\"text-align:center;\">\r\n\t<img src=\"img/uploads/20160606153316rDgq2PbwhNyBH64Q.jpg\" title=\"三星 智能冰箱\" alt=\"三星 智能冰箱\" data-ratio=\"1.1328125\" data-format=\"jpeg\"><span><em>三星 T9000 智能冰箱</em></span> \r\n</p>\r\n<p>\r\n</p>\r\n<div>\r\n</div>\r\n<p>\r\n\t<span style=\"text-align:start;\">你准备对着<a href=\"http://blogs.overdrive.com/devices/2013/01/11/ces-2013-ebooks-on-the-fridge-in-the-car-everywhere/\">三星冰箱 T9000</a> 站多久？这是要把人变成冰箱守门员的节奏。</span> \r\n</p>\r\n<h2>\r\n\t集成了自拍杆的小勺子\r\n</h2>\r\n<p style=\"text-align:start;\">\r\n</p>\r\n<p style=\"text-align:center;\">\r\n\t<img src=\"img/uploads/20160606153316pCl3w6SbIshijxL2.jpg\" title=\"Cinnamon Toast Crunch 的自拍勺\" alt=\"Cinnamon Toast Crunch 的自拍勺\" data-ratio=\"0.8707483\" data-format=\"jpeg\"><span><em>Cinnamon Toast Crunch 的自拍勺</em></span> \r\n</p>\r\n<p>\r\n</p>\r\n<p style=\"text-align:start;\">\r\n\t你要是想用 <a href=\"http://www.androidauthority.com/cinnamon-toast-crunch-selfie-spoon-free-643736/\" target=\"_blank\">Cinnamon Toast Crunch 出品的勺子</a>，请牢记，不要为了找个更好的拍照角度而把汤倒脸上了。\r\n</p>\r\n<p style=\"text-align:start;\">\r\n</p>\r\n<p>\r\n\t<span style=\"text-align:start;\">题图来自：<a href=\"http://www.studiodaily.com/2008/05/guavas-mark-wilhelm-on-crying-cg-tears/\" target=\"_blank\">StudioDaily</a></span> \r\n</p>\r\n<p>\r\n</p>\n\n\n"}